      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "SUPPA2 uses transcript quantification to compute inclusion values (PSI) of alternative splicing events across multiple samples.",
      "asbval:note": "The paper explicitly describes SUPPA2's core function of computing PSI values from transcript quantification. The research question accurately captures this functionality.",
